Dogan Yayin Ad-Sales Competition Hearing Will Begin March 29

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 
2011-02-12T10:12:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-12/dogan-yayin-ad-sales-competition-hearing-will-begin-march-29.html
  Dogan Yayin Holding AS , Turkey’s
biggest media company, said it will begin verbal arguments in an
inquiry by the country’s Competition Board into advertisement-
sales practices on March 29.  Dogan Yayin and its Hurriyet Gazetecilik & Matbaacilik AS,
Bagimsiz Gazeteciler Yayincilik AS and Dogan Daily News
Gazetecilik & Matbaacilik AS affiliates are subjects of the
investigation, the Istanbul-based company said in a stock-
exchange statement after markets closed yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at   barden@bloomberg.net . 